<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>607</hymn_number>
<title>zhǔ a wǒ suàn shén me 迦南607</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 zhǔ a wǒ suàn shén me nǐ jìng tái jǔ wǒ
 ràng wǒ zhàn zài nǐ miàn qián gěi nǐ chàng yī shǒu gē
 zhǔ a wǒ suàn shén me nǐ jìng gù niàn wǒ
 ràng wǒ shēng zài zhōng guó yíng jiē dà shōu gē
 dà fēng làng chōng zhe bī pò zhōng zǒu zhe
 nǐ ài wǒ bǎo hù wǒ yī zhí yǐn dǎo wǒ
 méi xiàng duàn xiàn de fēng zhēng méi xiàng diāo xiè de huā duǒ
 ràng wǒ chéng wèi shēng mìng de zhǒng zi zài nǐ lǐ miàn huó
 wǒ shēn shēn hū qiú nǐ nǐ yī dìng yào gěi wǒ zuò
 míng tiān jiāng huì yǒu jìng bài de gē shēng chōng mǎn měi yī gè jiǎo luò.</lyrics>
</song>